                              int pMounth,
                              int pYear)
        Registers a new product (book or magazine) with the given details.
        Parameters:
        id - The identifier of the product.
        name - The name of the product.
        numberPages - The number of pages in the product.
        review - The review of the product.
        genre - The genre of the product.
        price - The price of the product.
        category - The category of the product.
        periodicity - The periodicity of the product.
        typeProduct - The type of the product (1 for book, 2 for magazine).
        url - The URL of the product.
        pDay - The publication day of the product.
        pMonth - The publication month of the product.
        pYear - The publication year of the product.
        Returns:
        True if the product was successfully registered, false otherwise.
